data.title: 2005) – Find a Grave Gedenkstätte
data.meta_description: John Leon Helfrich   Web-posted Nov. 19, 11:49: AM   LAKEWOOD, CO ? John Leon Helfrich, 65, died Monday, November 14, 2005 at St. Anthony Central Hospital due to injuries sustained in a pedestrian/vehicle accident on November 1, 2005.  He was born August 17, 1940 to John T. and Laura E. (Droste) Helfrich in Spearville....
